Name: Click Real Fast
About the game: Ah, a nice, calm, in-depth game... is what you could say about literally any other game, except this one. A game so challenging you may need to seek medical attention, yet so simple you can play it with your eyes closed... as you should. Play with up to 100 friends (if you have that many) , and prove you have what it takes to Click Real Fast. Features Clicking Steam Workshop Multiplayer Clicking Blinding bloom effects Many Colors Clicking Deafening Music Special Effects Clicking Big Anger And much more! Test the lifespan of your mouse, keyboard, or controller, by Clicking... Real... FAST
